  <sect2 role="installation">
    <title>Instalao de Thunar</title>

    <para revision="sysv">
      First prevent the installation of an unneeded systemd file:
    </para>

<screen revision="sysv"><userinput>sed -i 's/\tinstall-systemd_userDATA/\t/' Makefile.in
</userinput></screen>

    <para>
      Instale <application>Thunar</application> executando os seguintes comandos:
    </para>

<screen><userinput>./configure --prefix=/usr \
            --sysconfdir=/etc \
            --docdir=/usr/share/doc/thunar-&thunar-version; &amp;&amp;
make</userinput></screen>

    <para>
      Esse pacote no vem com uma sute de teste.
    </para>

    <para>
      Agora, como o(a) usurio(a) <systemitem class="username">root</systemitem>:
    </para>

<screen role="root"><userinput>make install</userinput></screen>

  </sect2>

